      "text": "[illustration presented below in text form]\n\n------------------------------- linear time accidents AD 45 1610 1914 1974 etc I I I I Essence\n\nBIP: Morphological arrangement exploded in space + time. In a sense, therefore, space + time are not real; the contua are coaxial. They pervade one another: at least in terms of the abstraction to the morphological (Form axes) realm (#3 or #2). You go to the recovery of another accident along the Form axis (or all of them) by - as Plato says - anamnesis. I.",
